Now you tell me that what I'm doing is wrong, without looking at it from a legal standpoint. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uillystra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Illystra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 88<br> <font color=#333333>(4/21/02 12:59:17 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://watchkeepers.eva-01.net/nopst.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~&lt;//////////////////&gt;~ Happy 4/20 ~&lt;\\\\\\\\\\\</span><hr size=1> Harming another person, by nature, is wrong.<br>
